see the aftermath below you.

00:05:17.740 --> 00:05:21.460 position:56%
The north side of the river was more
badly affected than the south side

00:05:21.460 --> 00:05:24.820
and that's why people
are able to gain access.

00:05:24.820 --> 00:05:26.220
It's a little higher ground.

00:05:26.220 --> 00:05:29.110
But you can see the
extent of the water

00:05:29.110 --> 00:05:35.930 position:56%
