close to the height of the first,

00:05:35.930 --> 00:05:40.050
the first story of the cloister.

00:05:40.050 --> 00:05:45.420 position:56%
So all of the artwork that's at
that level was submerged underwater.

00:05:45.420 --> 00:05:51.440
Like a lot of emergencies
will have this recurrent theme

00:05:51.440 --> 00:05:57.900
