unexpectedly, they don't happen

00:05:57.900 --> 00:05:59.850
in a completely random way.

00:05:59.850 --> 00:06:04.810
Florence had had a series of
floods throughout the centuries.

00:06:04.810 --> 00:06:13.420
Easily four other major
floods in 1333, 1557, 1966,

00:06:13.420 --> 00:06:17.670
and 13 other minor
floods since 1557.

00:06:17.670 --> 00:06:24.510 position:56%
You can get a sense of the timing by
various markers throughout the city

00:06:24.510 --> 00:06:32.460
