the 1966 flood, 1333 flood,

00:06:32.460 --> 00:06:35.660
that these are certainly
witnesses as you're walking

00:06:35.660 --> 00:06:42.890
through the the town, looking up
close to 20 feet up of the extent

00:06:42.890 --> 00:06:45.730 position:56%
