00:09:14.300 --> 00:09:19.720
But he was, he came to head the
recovery, the long-term recovery

00:09:19.720 --> 00:09:24.100
and treatment of items
after the floods.

00:09:24.100 --> 00:09:30.300
So this is a lab that he
set up to start that work,

00:09:30.300 --> 00:09:33.860 position:56%
