00:10:16.320 --> 00:10:19.550
And I think this is something
that as we look back at Florence

00:10:19.550 --> 00:10:22.160
and we look at other
more recent emergencies,

00:10:22.160 --> 00:10:23.860
we should be more mindful of this

00:10:23.860 --> 00:10:26.880
