00:37:54.910 --> 00:37:57.920
Emergency management as a field,
as a profession didn't really start

00:37:57.920 --> 00:37:59.800
until the creation of FEMA.

00:37:59.800 --> 00:38:02.650
That notion of a comprehensive
approach,

00:38:02.650 --> 00:38:05.070
that notion of a scalable
