00:40:43.940 --> 00:40:47.260
If you suffer a major health
catastrophic event like a stroke

00:40:47.260 --> 00:40:50.800
or a heart attack and you
live, you fully expect

00:40:50.800 --> 00:40:52.920
that you will have a long
period of rehabilitation

00:40:52.920 --> 00:40:55.570
and you might not ever
fully recover.

00:40:55.570 --> 00:40:58.450
And that's a very similar
kind of approach

00:40:58.450 --> 00:41:01.270 position:56%
that happens with cultural property.

00:41:01.270 --> 00:41:05.460
It's going to take a long time.

00:41:05.460 --> 00:41:07.970
These stages overlap,
it's very confusing,

00:41:07.970 --> 00:41:12.950
