00:49:53.440 --> 00:49:58.030
and essentially information and
documents that people could use.

00:49:58.030 --> 00:50:00.540
But it was not really
a proactive responder

00:50:00.540 --> 00:50:04.120
in the sense of emergencies.

00:50:04.120 --> 00:50:09.070 position:56%
And it really has transformed itself
into a group of organizations,

00:50:09.070 --> 00:50:11.030
Library of Congress is one of them,

00:50:11.030 --> 00:50:16.790
