00:55:09.720 --> 00:55:13.060
The reason that we don't have as
much work on emergency planning

00:55:13.060 --> 00:55:16.240
as we should is I think because
staffs are under a lot of pressure

00:55:16.240 --> 00:55:18.810
and staffs are generally
below the high watermark

00:55:18.810 --> 00:55:21.800
that they had in better times.

00:55:21.800 --> 00:55:25.420
It's going to be real
hard to create those plans

00:55:25.420 --> 00:55:27.490
